        "javadoc": "/**\n * Simple constructor.\n * Build a vector from its azimuthal coordinates\n * @param alpha azimuth (&alpha;) around Z\n *              (0 is +X, &pi;/2 is +Y, &pi; is -X and 3&pi;/2 is -Y)\n * @param delta elevation (&delta;) above (XY) plane, from -&pi;/2 to +&pi;/2\n * @see #getAlpha()\n * @see #getDelta()\n */\n",
